Malice/ Hellplague:
 
After Blacknightmare left to get the new sensor, Hellplague reached into Malice's exposed chest.  She drummed her fingers on his spark chamber.  Malice took a sharp breath, it really freaked him out to have someone touching his spark chamber.  Hellplague giggled and laid down next Malice.  He looked at her with a mix expression of relief and suprise.
"Please, don't do that.  It feels really weird." he said.
Hellplague grinned and the moved in to kiss him.  As she did, her hand reurned to drumming on his spark chamber.  Their lips met, and Malice was motionless.  Hellplague enjoyed the act, and deepened the kiss.
